@startuml
!include theme.iuml
title STrans 部署架构图
top to bottom direction

actor "普通用户/管理员" as User

cloud "视频与外部数据" {
  node "固定沙盘摄像头" as Camera
  node "手机/USB/本地录像" as Mobile
  node "天气/可选智能报告 API" as External
}

node "浏览器终端" as Browser {
  artifact "React + Vite SPA" as React
  artifact "道路建模静态页" as ModelerPage
}

node "Windows 应用主机" as Host {
  component "FastAPI\nREST + MJPEG" as API
  component "CameraHub / VideoStreamService" as Video
  component "LocalModel / RoadAnomaly / RoadMask" as Vision
  component "RoadLogic / Scheduler" as Traffic
  component "Auth / Whitelist / Analysis / Report" as Business
  database "SQLite" as DB
  folder "模型权重" as Weights
  folder "告警证据与导出" as Evidence
  component "可选 localhost:8765\nRTSP 截帧桥接" as Bridge
}

node "NVIDIA GPU" as GPU {
  component "CUDA 12.6\nYOLO / SegFormer" as CUDA
}

User -down-> React : HTTPS/HTTP
React -down-> API : REST + MJPEG
React --> ModelerPage : 管理员入口
Camera --> Video : RTSP/MJPEG
Mobile --> Video : HTTP/设备/文件
Video --> API
API --> Vision : JPEG 帧
Vision -down-> GPU : 本地推理
Weights --> Vision
Vision --> Traffic : 检测/轨迹/异常
Traffic --> Business : 交通状态/事件
Business --> DB
Business --> Evidence
API --> External : 可选调用
ModelerPage --> Bridge : 可选 RTSP 单帧
ModelerPage --> Traffic : 经审核 JSON 配置

note bottom of Bridge
  只绑定 127.0.0.1，
  无鉴权，不对局域网开放。
end note
@enduml
